data.description: Welcome to your charming new home at 2240 Ben Blvd! This manufactured home is IMMACULATE. Love and care went into maintaining & upgrading this home and it truly shows. Newer laminated flooring throughout. NO CARPET! The finishes of the home are modern & rustic. Lots of natural light throughout. The Generac generator is included & a MUST in Texas. This is a HUGE VALUE. Updated fencing encloses the backyard. COVERED back patio is the perfect place for entertaining! The shed in the backyard is SIZABLE & will offer really convenient storage for a lucky buyer. This home offers true value. Come see it & get your offer in today!
